Step 1: Find the value of k . ex : f(i) = f(i-1) + f(i-4) ,k =4
Step 2 : Find out the first k terms .and call this as F1 vector ex : [0 1] for fibonacci
Step 3 : Find the transformation matrix 'T' (k X k)
          such that T X Fi  = F(i+1)
          ex for fibonacci T= [[0 1][1 1]]   Fi = [ F(i-2) F[i-1) ],   Fi+1 =  T X  Fi = [ F(i-1) F(i) ]
          Fn =  pow( T, n-1) X F(1)   // O(k^3 log(N))
 --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
          for f(i) = f(i-1) +  4 . f(i-2)  + 3 . f(i-3) + f(i-4)
 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------         
T(k x k)             0 1 0 0                                        Fi be like             f(i-4)                      F(i+1) =T X Fi
                     0 0 1 0                                                               f(i-3)
                     0 0 0 1                                                               f(i-2)
                     1 3 4 1                                                               f(i-1)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                     
         For variations like   f(i) = f(i-1) +  4 . f(i-2)  + 3 . f(i-3) + f(i-4) + d
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
T be like            0 1 0 0 0                                      Fi be like              f(i-4)                      F(i+1) =T X Fi
                     0 0 1 0 0                                                              f(i-3)
                     0 0 0 1 0                                                              f(i-2)
                     1 4 3 1 1                                                              f(i-1)  
                     0 0 0 0 1                                                                 d             
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
C[i] [j] +=  A[i] [x] * B[x] [j]
